               Abstract
               
                  The results of an SCF Xα SW calculation of Pt L1 and L2,3 X-ray absorption spectra in the complexes PtCl4
                     2− and PtCl6
                     2− at photoelectron energies from −20 to + 210 eV have revealed the main details of the pre-edge structure and the origins of XANES and EXAFS.
               
